{"tid":2497529,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【寸TVB上位】193郭嘉駿想做米線代言人　譚仔三哥：正聯絡花姐","createTime":"2021-04-20T14:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T15:20:47.000Z","uid":212249,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18dd75e39735ef29d3396a043d889142381e6abf","tid":2497529,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2021-04-19-15-40-54NyEeTc3Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2021-04-19-15-40-54NyEeTc3Z.jpg&h=c8ec4ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全民造星出身的 ERROR 成員 193（郭嘉駿），早前因寸無綫的言論人氣急升，被網民大讚敢言。昨日 ERROR 出席 ViuTV《Chill Club》頒獎禮，193 就直言自己想做米線代言人，令一眾粉絲即發起「我要193代言譚仔三哥」行動！<br />\n<br />\n昨日 ERROR 出席《Chill Club》頒獎禮，成員肥仔及阿Dee受訪時指笑指 193 是隊內的大爺，一直叫他做「三爺」，但 193 則指還是比較想大家叫他「三哥」，因為想接米線店代言；193 又再寸 TVB 欲力棒的「千禧五虎」，稱「五虎」這個詞很老土，「不如我哋（ERROR）叫四隻白虎啦！可以有好多脫毛贊助。」<br />\n<br />\n193 開到聲，一眾粉絲就落力為他完成心願，立即發起「我要193代言譚仔三哥」行動，湧入米線店譚仔三哥的社交網以「洗版式」留言，強烈要求譚仔三哥找他擔任新代言人，又指 193 喜歡吃鮑魚，建議可以推出「193鮑片米線」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2021-04-19-15-45-31Bpz7RxQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2021-04-19-15-45-31Bpz7RxQn.jpg&h=74084782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n向來公關反應快的譚仔三哥，也火速收到網友要求，回覆「打緊比（畀）花姐， 三哥巧（好）有feel」，粉絲們都表示期待雙方的合作。譚仔三哥以往亦曾請 100毛的盤菜瑩子、憑 ViuTV《調教你男友》走紅的魏浚笙（Jeffrey）賣廣告，相信是次邀請 193 擔任代言，成事機會極高！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2021-04-19-15-45-46MoyRTvuS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2021-04-19-15-45-46MoyRTvuS.png&h=8ac29880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n193 早前回應曾志偉指 ViuTV 收視低言論，表示「（無綫）收視點得嗰幾百部電視機，我哋不嬲都唔介意」，又暗寸 J2 台無新血「40幾歲仲做後生仔傾偈」，大膽言論獲網友激讚，認為他的反駁大快人心，Instagram 追蹤者更因此急升幾萬。"},{"pid":"277c25d229525fc03b6d8da643b20b5afd533145","tid":2497529,"uid":212249,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/entertainment/player?newsId=431652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431652&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ6T%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=d6253680\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431652&h=3122b253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/entertainment/player?newsId=431652</a><br />\n<br />\n啲fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8dc5a134385c7c31139018d3f5e6429709d41c","tid":2497529,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:54:58.000Z","msg":"三哥啲PR 好屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a3e7bed4ddc5e3aa9dc9f5f9b85cc5331d56b2","tid":2497529,"uid":116967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定會日日食<br />\n飲藍妹食三哥"},{"pid":"f1ba1735f0bf530de06ed6a6751d244ab738a7b1","tid":2497529,"uid":325210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da3e1fbf53a1cb87f7512dd1172abf365c36f82","tid":2497529,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" cl